instruction: Develop an HTML page from scratch introducing a pet store.
output:
Welcome to Our Pet Store

We are the one-stop shop for all of your pet needs!

Whether you're interested in buying a pet for the first time, looking for pet supplies, veterinarian services, or want to make sure your pet feels loved with some treats, we've got you covered.
